            <p>All contents of this website are Copyright Â© 2023 Tebra Technologies, Inc. All Rights Reserved. All logos are trademarks and service marks of Tebra Technologies, Inc. All other trademarks, service marks and logos used in this Site are the property of their respective owners.</p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
            <p>Please contact us:</p>
            <ul class="list-none space-y-2 mt-2">
              <li><strong>Phone:</strong> 301-750-9771</li>
              <li><strong>Mail:</strong> 1328 Southern Ave SE, Suite 205, Washington, DC 20032</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose p {
    @apply text-gray-600 mb-4;
  }
  .prose {
    @apply space-y-4;
  }
  .prose ul {
    @apply text-gray-600;
  }
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-gray-800;
  }
  .uppercase {
    @apply tracking-wide text-sm;
  }
</style>